# ============================================================
# .gitignore
# ============================================================
# Role: Tier 2 — Orchestration (repository hygiene)
# Purpose: Prevents secrets and runtime state from being
#          committed: node_modules/ (npm install artifacts),
#          venv/ (Python virtualenv), data/ (SQLite memory.db),
#          and .env (DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN and NVIDIA_API_KEY).
# Calls:   none (consumed by git itself).
# Used by: git, on every status/add/commit.
# ============================================================
node_modules/
data/
.env
venv
